data.description:
Awesome Riverside/Avondale Downtown property available for rent in this roomy duplex. Upstairs unit furnished and available for mid term and annual rentals. Big yard, spacious unit, plus internet included for your convenience. May I add washer and dryer as well. This unit will not last long so don't wait.

Comes fully furnished
No smoking allowed inside
Small dogs are allowed 
Pet fee does apply $350
Short term, mid term, annual leases
